## ğŸ“‘ Overview  
AngelCam is an **AI-powered baby monitoring system** that uses object detection to identify and track babies in surveillance video footage. If a baby exits a defined safe zone, the system **raises an alert**. This solution is ideal for busy parents and can be integrated into nanny cams or smart surveillance systems.  

---

## ğŸ¯ Features  
- ğŸ¼ Real-time **baby detection & tracking**  
- ğŸ–¼ï¸ Define a **custom safe zone**  
- ğŸš¨ Alert if baby moves outside the safe zone  
- ğŸ“Š Detection history & monitoring logs  

---

## âš™ï¸ Tech Stack  
- **Programming Language**: Python  
- **Model**: YOLOv5 (Object Detection)  
- **Dataset**: Baby Detection (Roboflow)  
- **Environment**: Google Colab (GPU Enabled)  

---

## ğŸš€ How It Works  
1. Load the trained **YOLOv5 model**  
2. Stream video from webcam / surveillance feed  
3. Detect and track the baby inside the frame  
4. If the baby exits the **safe zone**, an **alert is triggered**  

